{"tid":2462154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）CCTVB 辭左職個王俊彥831太子有份直播 當時話只係見到班速龍揮舞警棍","createTime":"2021-03-25T23:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T00:57:55.000Z","uid":25240,"like":203,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"04a88ee58cacde128d31ad41ac18880c6809f32c","tid":2462154,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:41:24.000Z","msg":"成班on9 見佢打篇煽情文跳船就當正佢好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6SDBSAl0Ebo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6SDBSAl0Ebo&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=3db1815b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6SDBSAl0Ebo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n03:11 頭先就係有速龍小隊既人  <br />\n我地見過就係<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">揮動警棍同埋發射催淚水劑</span></span><br />\n<br />\n08:21 剛才係中環方向列車既警察係作出拘捕行動 <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">都有d混亂架 </span></span><br />\n防暴警察都係有揮動警棍同埋施放過催淚水劑<br />\n有部分乘客或者市者情緒都係相當激動 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問下你班吹奏呢條賤種既人係咪唔撚記得曬cctvb過去一年九個月點樣抹黑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話袁花唔係仆街<br />\n但成個真理部250人 <br />\n冇下面班走狗配合點一年365 日 24小時候全天候抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dd0ea0b4b4b6ece520d0b69e3c884ec3c62087","tid":2462154,"uid":7820,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:45:05.000Z","msg":"真啊 唔知點解有班人好鍾意一廂情願覺得呢啲仆街係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053feb22992fb375c5250968041b4bc8fcd37e9d","tid":2462154,"uid":25240,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:45:58.000Z","msg":"以下節錄部份話人「鬥黃」言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 王俊彥都係 跟稿讀<br />\n佢無辜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91X1fq9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91X1fq9.png&h=857c6041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我相信呢6條友都係被鄧炳強「迫」<br />\n尤其係cctvb 出身<span class=\"red\">劉肇邦</span> 警司 同 <span class=\"red\">鄒昊享</span> 督察<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph0Fv0K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph0Fv0K.jpg&h=606400b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcu7a0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdcu7a0L.jpg&h=a068d23f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tj2gONq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftj2gONq.jpg&h=0a370a68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mciGZT5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmciGZT5.jpg&h=db8dfc2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 同d 魚毛蝦兵黎同 pk tang / 速龍比<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來可以access 到大氣電波都魚毛蝦兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁退一步黎講 防暴最多人個期 ～6k人<br />\n速龍要其他special ops 隊抽調 我估max 200人以內<br />\n再加便衣狗 實際出過行動既最多一萬人 <br />\n其他一律後勤 / 文職   冇實際落場打人<br />\n叫「三萬死全家」又算唔算鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本你班選擇性搬龍門既先係最鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LY3WOOS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLY3WOOS.png&h=4a71af0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d7f1f65253abf08b1bef0679b231a822133e340","tid":2462154,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ad5e6c6903347cc3e8fdcc2a6d0b405d354ac0","tid":2462154,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:46:17.000Z","msg":"希望大家會支持退休警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1b74d8875258b4247eea8ec8054ace923bd650","tid":2462154,"uid":8830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da57545a81096c53a1c1c0ffc661456e26abfb56","tid":2462154,"uid":25240,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"48dd0ea0b4b4b6ece520d0b69e3c884ec3c62087","tid":2462154,"uid":7820,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:45:05.000Z","msg":"真啊 唔知點解有班人好鍾意一廂情願覺得呢啲仆街係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:48:16.000Z","msg":"都話班垃圾只係 選擇性去判斷一條友 「好人」<br />\n達叔做護旗手 = 佢電影成就高唔應該落井下石<br />\n但一提成龍就話兩者唔可以直接比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本班友先係最雙重標準個堆<br />\n發覺自己套標準唔fit 落佢地鍾意既人度就搬龍門<br />\n然後屌人鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e347492a1be694bb44dfb0cf50a49ed6e0e168b","tid":2462154,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:48:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f18e95f5359bbfe55e98355733f3b9ab6ce22464","tid":2462154,"uid":41423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:49:30.000Z","msg":"準備考白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290a328402b2e4cdc57af0557b292865eea4f07a","tid":2462154,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad69358843f30b6e4155c4226f3ef7a3b795218","tid":2462154,"uid":25240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f18e95f5359bbfe55e98355733f3b9ab6ce22464","tid":2462154,"uid":41423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:49:30.000Z","msg":"準備考白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:50:58.000Z","msg":"如果真係考白衫就真係炒到應一應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b5f8ce8af7bc40b133acdb3e53bc6b4c38b67a","tid":2462154,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969ba24ccd393dbdb7e35339b4ef5f29de06